## Current System Status

The application currently supports:

- Add task dialog
- Edit task dialog
- Delete task with confirmation
- Mark Complete toggle
- Warning alerts when no task is selected
- JSON persistence ... save + load automatically
- Tasks load on startup
- Tasks save after Add/Edit/Delete/Complete

Current architecture:

Main.java: UI layer  
TaskRow.java: model  
TaskStorage.java: persistence layer  
(TaskService.java: backend service layer in progress)
